#: ../../../topics/spider-middleware.rst:145
msgid ""
"This method is called when a spider or :meth:`process_spider_output` method "
"(from a previous spider middleware) raises an exception."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/spider-middleware.rst:148
msgid ""
":meth:`process_spider_exception` should return either ``None`` or an "
"iterable of :class:`~scrapy.Request` or :ref:`item <topics-items>` objects."
